                Swiss Zoological Society
          .col-md-3.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
            = link_to 'http://http://www.swiss-systematics.ch/', id: "logos-sponsors-sss", target: '_blank', class: "logos-logo" do
              %span.logos-log-title
                Swiss Systematics Society
